\c 1
\s Umbiko wokufa kukaSawuli
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi emva kokufa kukaSawuli, uDavida esephendukile ekutshayeni amaAmaleki, uDavida wahlala insuku ezimbili eZikilagi\x + 1 Sam. 30.17,26.\x*.
\v 2 Kwasekusithi ngosuku lwesithathu, khangela, kwafika umuntu evela enkambeni evela kuSawuli\x + 4.10.\x*, ozigqoko zakhe zazidatshuliwe\x + 1.11. 1 Sam. 4.12. Gen. 44.13.\x*, \add e\add*lenhlabathi ekhanda lakhe. Kwasekusithi efika kuDavida wawela emhlabathini, wakhonza\x + Josh. 7.6.\x*.
\v 3 UDavida wasesithi kuye: Uvela ngaphi? Wasesithi kuye: Ngiphephile enkambeni yakoIsrayeli\x + 1.13. Gen. 16.8.\x*.
\v 4 UDavida wasesithi kuye: Lunjani udaba? Akungitshele. Wasesithi: Abantu babalekile empini, labanengi babantu labo bawile njalo bafile, uSawuli laye loJonathani indodana yakhe labo bafile.
\v 5 UDavida wasesithi kulelojaha elalimbikela: Wazi njani ukuthi uSawuli loJonathani indodana yakhe bafile?
\v 6 Lelojaha elalimbikela laselisithi: Kuthe ngisithi thutshu entabeni yeGilibowa, khangela, uSawuli eyeme emkhontweni wakhe, khangela-ke, inqola labagadi bamabhiza kwakumnamathele\x + 1 Sam. 31.1-4.\x*.
\v 7 Lapho enyemukula, wasengibona, wangibiza; ngasengisithi: Khangela ngi\add lapha\add*.
\v 8 Wasesithi kimi: Ungubani? Ngasengisithi kuye: NgingumAmaleki.
\v 9 Wasesithi kimi: Ake ume phezu kwami ungibulale; ngoba ubuhlungu obukhulu bungehlele, ngoba impilo yami isaphelele kimi.
\v 10 Ngakho ngema phezu kwakhe ngambulala, ngoba ngazi ukuthi angeke aphile emva kokuwa kwakhe. Ngasengithatha umqhele owawusekhanda lakhe\x + 2 Kho. 11.12. Hlab. 89.39. 132.18.\x*, lesongo elalisengalweni yakhe, ngikulethile lapha enkosini yami\x + Nani 31.50.\x*.
\v 11 UDavida wasebamba izigqoko zakhe wazidabula, njalo lawo wonke amadoda ayelaye\x + 1.11. 1 Sam. 4.12. Gen. 44.13.\x*.
\v 12 Basebelila, bakhala inyembezi, bazila ukudla kwaze kwahlwa ngenxa kaSawuli, langenxa kaJonathani indodana yakhe, langenxa yabantu beN\nd kosi\nd*, langenxa yendlu kaIsrayeli, ngoba babewe ngenkemba.
\p
\v 13 UDavida wasesithi kulelojaha elalimbikele: Uvela ngaphi? Laselisithi: Ngiyindodana yomuntu wezizweni, umAmaleki.
\v 14 UDavida wasesithi kulo: Kawesabanga njani\x + 1 Sam. 31.4.\x* ukwelula isandla sakho ukubhubhisa\x + 1 Sam. 24.6. 26.9. Hlab. 105.15.\x* ogcotshiweyo weN\nd kosi\x + 1 Sam. 12.3.\x*\nd*?
\v 15 UDavida wasebiza elinye lamajaha, wathi: Sondela ulidumele. Laselilitshaya laze lafa\x + 4.10,12.\x*.
\v 16 UDavida wasesithi kulo: Igazi lakho kalibe phezu kwekhanda lakho\x + Josh. 2.19. 1 Kho. 2.37. Levi 20.9.\x*; ngoba umlomo wakho ufakaze umelene lawe\x + 1.10. Luka 19.22.\x*, usithi: Mina ngimbulele ogcotshiweyo weN\nd kosi\x + 1 Sam. 12.3.\x*\nd*.
\s Isililo sikaDavida ngoSawuli loJonathani
\p
\v 17 UDavida waselila lesisililo ngenxa kaSawuli loJonathani indodana yakhe\x + 3.33. 2 Lan. 35.25. Hez. 27.32. 32.16.\x*
\v 18 (lapho wathi kufundiswe abantwana bakoJuda "IDandili"; khangela, kubhaliwe egwalweni lukaJashari)\x + 1 Sam. 31.3.\x*:
\p
\v 19 Ubuhle bukaIsrayeli bubulewe ezindaweni zakho eziphakemeyo. Awe njani amaqhawe\x + 1.25,27.\x*!
\v 20 Lingakukhulumi eGathi\x + 1 Sam. 31.9. Mika 1.10. 1 Sam. 17.4.\x*, lingakumemezeli ezitaladeni zeAshikeloni\x + Hlu. 1.18. Hlu. 16.23.\x*, hlezi athokoze amadodakazi amaFilisti\x + Eks. 15.20. Hlu. 11.34. 1 Sam. 18.6.\x*, hlezi ajabule amadodakazi abangasokwanga\x + Hlu. 14.3.\x*.
\v 21 Zintaba zeGilibowa, kakungabi khona amazolo kumbe izulu phezu kwenu\x + 1 Sam. 31.1.\x*, kumbe amasimu eminikelo. Ngoba izihlangu zamaqhawe zangcoliswa khona; isihlangu sikaSawuli singagcotshwanga ngamafutha\x + 1 Sam. 10.1.\x*
\v 22 egazini lababuleweyo, emahwahweni amaqhawe idandili likaJonathani kaliphendukanga, lenkemba kaSawuli kayibuyelanga ize\x + 1 Sam. 18.4.\x*.
\v 23 USawuli loJonathani babethandeka bebahle empilweni zabo, lekufeni kwabo kabehlukaniswanga; babelesiqubu kulezinkozi\x + Jer. 4.13. Hab. 1.8.\x*, belamandla kulezilwane\x + Hlu. 14.18.\x*.
\v 24 Madodakazi akoIsrayeli, mkhaleleni inyembezi uSawuli, owaligqokisa ngokubomvu lentokozo, owafaka imiceciso yegolide phezu kwezigqoko zenu\x + Eks. 33.4,5,6. Hez. 7.20. 16.7,11.\x*.
\v 25 Awe njani amaqhawe phakathi kwempi! Jonathani, \add u\add*bulewe endaweni zakho eziphakemeyo!
\v 26 Ngidabukile ngawe, mfowethu Jonathani; ubumnandi kakhulu kimi, uthando lwakho belumangalisa kimi lusedlula uthando lwabesifazana\x + 1 Sam. 18.1. 1 Sam. 23.16.\x*.
\v 27 Awe njani amaqhawe, zabhubha lezikhali zempi\x + 1.19,25.\x*!
